A collection of items from Cecil B. DeMille films, including The Ten Commandments, will be sold later this week by New Hampshire based RR Auction.

The highlight of the collection is 15 previously unpublished 35mm color slides from the set of the 1956 classic.

Elsewhere unsigned oil paintings created by The Ten Commandments' make-up supervisor Wally Westmore and commissioned directly by DeMille are up for sale.

